text:
After recent renovations, the store feels much cleaner and spacious as compared to its pre-renovation state, great improvements.

However, it would seem as though there are fewer items to purchase as compared to their pre-renovation times.

Nonetheless, same owner as before, service is always good and welcoming.

It's a huge convenient store/ supermarket which sells beverages,foods,ingredients,snacks and fruits at a low price and added discount! But it is not airconditioned and it is really plain with a simple design.
